an isolating membrane,

285
00:23:11,730 --> 00:23:13,400
a catalyst.

286
00:23:13,400 --> 00:23:15,710
They occupy half of the cost.

287
00:23:15,710 --> 00:23:18,690
But membranless battery,

288
00:23:20,030 --> 00:23:22,270
they not only don't need isolating membranes,

