00:31:14,690 --> 00:31:16,810
[I'm Gu Xiaoling. I can't pay back my debt. So I'm willing to have sex with you. ¥300 per night. The price is negotiable if you are introduced by friends. I'm driven desperate now. Please help me.]

400
00:31:24,680 --> 00:31:27,490
Don't cry. Talk.

401
00:31:27,490 --> 00:31:29,400
Say something.

402
00:31:36,780 --> 00:31:39,180
I needed money,

403
00:31:39,180 --> 00:31:42,900
so I found a company and borrowed ¥100,000.

404
00:31:46,560 --> 00:31:48,690
If you needed money, why didn't you come to me?

405
00:31:48,690 --> 00:31:51,650
You helped me return ¥130,000 just recently. I couldn't just ask for more.

406
00:31:51,650 --> 00:31:53,560
And then?

407
00:31:54,730 --> 00:31:56,480
I said I'd borrow ¥100,000,

408
00:31:56,480 --> 00:31:59,940
and return ¥140,000 in two years, ¥6,000 a month.

409
00:31:59,940 --> 00:32:04,710
I don't know how it became six thousand a week.

410
00:32:04,710 --> 00:32:06,940
How is that possible?

411
00:32:07,780 --> 00:32:11,990
When I signed the contract, I didn't look very carefully at what it said.

412
00:32:12,940 --> 00:32:15,010
It's such an important thing, how could you not pay attention?

413
00:32:15,010 --> 00:32:18,720
The contract was so thick, how was I supposed to read it all?

414
00:32:19,620 --> 00:32:21,800
Then you deserve it!

415
00:32:23,990 --> 00:32:28,240
Sister Siyu, don't scold Xiaoling. She's already upset enough as is.

416
00:32:33,890 --> 00:32:37,220
They came asking for money yesterday.

417
00:32:37,220 --> 00:32:40,470
I didn't have it, so they...

418
00:32:41,720 --> 00:32:47,630
Everyone in my contact list got this message. How am I supposed to face them?

419
00:33:03,400 --> 00:33:04,600
Who are you guys looking for?

420
00:33:04,600 --> 00:33:09,400
Ms. Gu, you've got friends over? That's perfect.

421
00:33:09,400 --> 00:33:12,200
So, can you return the money today?

422
00:33:12,200 --> 00:33:13,600
I can't return it.

423
00:33:13,600 --> 00:33:15,400
Get your friends to let you borrow some then.

424
00:33:15,400 --> 00:33:18,000
If you send a message like that, who would possibly want to help me?

425
00:33:18,000 --> 00:33:20,400
Wow. You're quite stubborn.

426
00:33:20,400 --> 00:33:24,200
Let me tell you. If you can't return it today, I've got an even bigger trick up my sleeve.

427
00:33:24,200 --> 00:33:26,400
Why are you so rude?

428
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:28,800
We're trying to solve Ms. Gu's problem.

429
00:33:28,800 --> 00:33:30,800
Not scare them.

430
00:33:32,200 --> 00:33:37,400
Ms. Gu, if you really can't return it, I'll help you.

431
00:33:37,400 --> 00:33:40,800
You can get another company and borrow money from them.

432
00:33:40,800 --> 00:33:42,200
Return ours first.

433
00:33:42,200 --> 00:33:44,000
You're full of tricks.

434
00:33:44,000 --> 00:33:45,800
You definitely can't.

435
00:33:45,800 --> 00:33:47,400
Then you help her return it.

436
00:33:47,400 --> 00:33:50,400
Exactly! It's a total of ¥106,000.

437
00:33:50,400 --> 00:33:52,000
Get the money.

438
00:33:52,000 --> 00:33:57,400
Ms. Gu, you already know our methods.

439
00:33:57,400 --> 00:33:59,800
I even came up with a plan for you.

440
00:33:59,800 --> 00:34:02,600
The rest is up to you.

441
00:34:04,000 --> 00:34:04,800
Let's go.

442
00:34:04,800 --> 00:34:07,100
We will come back tomorrow.

443
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:14,000
You guys purposefully tricked Gu Xiaoling in the contract. She's an idiot and doesn't understand, so that's on her,

444
00:34:14,000 --> 00:34:18,000
but running into her house smashing and breaking everything is wrong.

445
00:34:18,000 --> 00:34:20,000
What do you want to do?

446
00:34:21,800 --> 00:34:26,600
Right now. I'm about to report you for violent robbery and debt collection.

447
00:34:26,600 --> 00:34:28,000
I'm going to kill you.

448
00:34:28,000 --> 00:34:31,600
If I add assault and battery, you'll be stuck in jail for ten years at least. If that doesn't happen, then my last name isn't Li!

449
00:34:31,600 --> 00:34:33,800
Miss, that would be framing us.

450
00:34:33,800 --> 00:34:35,400
Yes. I am framing you.

451
00:34:35,400 --> 00:34:38,400
You think you're the only two gangsters on this earth?

452
00:34:38,400 --> 00:34:40,000
Zhizhi, call the police!

453
00:34:40,000 --> 00:34:41,400
Don't move! Who dares to move?

454
00:34:41,400 --> 00:34:43,200
Xiaoling, go to the window and scream for help.

455
00:34:43,200 --> 00:34:45,600
Don't move. Get over here.

456
00:34:45,600 --> 00:34:47,200
Help! Help!

457
00:34:47,200 --> 00:34:50,000
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

458
00:34:51,900 --> 00:34:54,800
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

459
00:34:54,800 --> 00:34:57,400
We were too rash.

460
00:34:57,400 --> 00:35:00,700
We'll apologize. Okay?

461
00:35:02,200 --> 00:35:05,600
Miss, we're also doing this for business.

462
00:35:05,600 --> 00:35:08,600
Why would you put us in such a place?

463
00:35:08,600 --> 00:35:13,100
If Ms. Gu is willing to return the money, then everything will be fine.

464
00:35:13,100 --> 00:35:17,800
We will definitely pay back the money including the interest by this week.

465
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:22,000
You guys must apologize and immediately send a text to help Xiaoling regain her reputation,

466
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:24,200
and promise to never bother her again.

467
00:35:24,200 --> 00:35:25,400
But...

468
00:35:25,400 --> 00:35:27,000
There is nothing to discuss.

469
00:35:27,000 --> 00:35:28,800
Okay.

470
00:35:29,600 --> 00:35:31,400
Sorry.

471
00:35:35,700 --> 00:35:37,700
Send the message.

472
00:35:37,700 --> 00:35:39,500
I will, I will.

473
00:35:42,100 --> 00:35:46,800
You, clean up the mess you made.

474
00:35:46,800 --> 00:35:50,400
- I.. You... 
 - Xiao Wu, just do it.

475
00:35:51,400 --> 00:35:53,800
Okay.

476
00:36:04,000 --> 00:36:08,000
[I talked nonsense today. I apologize to Ms. Gu.]

477
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:09,800
Get lost.

478
00:36:31,200 --> 00:36:35,000
Sister Siyu, you're so formidable.

479
00:36:53,800 --> 00:36:58,200
Siyu... thank you.

480
00:36:59,840 --> 00:37:04,400
Why would you borrow so much money?

481
00:37:04,400 --> 00:37:08,400
I signed up for a seminar that cost ¥100,000 as tuition.

482
00:37:08,400 --> 00:37:10,200
To learn what?

483
00:37:10,200 --> 00:37:13,400
Art appreciation and management.

484
00:37:14,400 --> 00:37:17,200
Are you crazy?

485
00:37:17,200 --> 00:37:21,200
I'm not crazy. It was a clearheaded decision.

486
00:37:22,400 --> 00:37:26,000
Our club has started group buying, and the people who come are getting worse and worse.

487
00:37:26,000 --> 00:37:28,000
I need to change groups.

488
00:37:28,000 --> 00:37:32,000
I don't think you need to change groups, you need to change brains!

489
00:37:32,000 --> 00:37:33,600
What's wrong?

490
00:37:33,600 --> 00:37:36,200
You already suffered so much from Lan Ke, why didn't you learn from that?

491
00:37:36,200 --> 00:37:39,000
How come all you think about is shortcuts?

492
00:37:39,000 --> 00:37:41,000
What do you mean shortcuts?

493
00:37:41,000 --> 00:37:43,800
Besides, shortcuts are made for people to walk on!

494
00:37:43,800 --> 00:37:46,000
Why can't it be me?

495
00:37:46,000 --> 00:37:48,400
You need to have the skill to walk a shortcut! What skill do you have?

496
00:37:48,400 --> 00:37:50,000
Do you think rich people are all idiots?

497
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:52,000
You think you can do whatever you want just because you're pretty?

498
00:37:52,000 --> 00:37:55,000
Siyu, don't act like you're allowed to lecture me just because you helped me return the money.

499
00:37:55,000 --> 00:37:56,200
Not only did I help you return the money,

500
00:37:56,200 --> 00:37:59,000
but I also helped you return your debt! I have the right to lecture you.

501
00:37:59,000 --> 00:38:01,000
I don't need you to return it for me!

502
00:38:01,000 --> 00:38:02,600
That's what you said.

503
00:38:02,600 --> 00:38:05,200
From today on, even if I die on the street, I still won't ask you to help me!

504
00:38:05,200 --> 00:38:08,600
From today on, anyone who ever helps you again is sick in the head!

505
00:38:11,200 --> 00:38:12,200
Sister Siyu!

506
00:38:12,200 --> 00:38:14,700
Zhizhi, don't stop her.

507
00:38:15,800 --> 00:38:17,600
Xiaoling.

508
00:38:22,400 --> 00:38:24,400
Xiaoling.

509
00:39:15,800 --> 00:39:18,700
Take a look.

510
00:39:25,200 --> 00:39:27,400
Siyu just gave me ¥110,000.

511
00:39:27,400 --> 00:39:29,800
She told me to give it to you.

512
00:39:29,800 --> 00:39:33,000
She said you should hurry and return it to those people.

513
00:39:39,200 --> 00:39:45,000
Siyu was just saying that stuff. In her heart, she still loves you.

514
00:40:07,380 --> 00:40:09,220
Li Siyu,

515
00:40:10,200 --> 00:40:14,800
don't you dare think that just because you helped me, I'll bow down to you.

516
00:40:15,400 --> 00:40:18,200
I will definitely return ten times the amount back to you.

517
00:40:18,200 --> 00:40:21,700
But I never want to see you again.

518
00:42:22,600 --> 00:42:25,600
I made you a wonderful dinner.

519
00:42:29,000 --> 00:42:34,400
I'm too tired today. I'll go see you some other day.

